text: The Cathedral of Sigüenza () is a cathedral in Guadalajara, Spain. It was declared Bien de Interés Cultural in 1931. It is built in Romanesque and Gothic style. The cathedral is the seat of the Roman Catholic Diocese of Sigüenza-Guadalajara. File:Siguviae.jpg|Cathedral of Sigüenza. File:Presbiterio.jpg|Vaults of the presbytery and the transept.
